OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FPatchy cloud and sunny spells
OL,6,Fexpected for much of the day with most
OL,7,Fareas staying dry, although isolated
OL,8,Flight showers are possible. Breezy.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,11,FGenerally dry through this period with
OL,12,Fpatchy cloud and sunny spells. Breezy
OL,13,Fon Saturday but winds falling light
OL,14,Ffor Sunday and Monday. Feeling warm,
OL,15,Fespecially in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
